95
00:05:42,200 --> 00:05:47,059
" [The Balrog] drew itself up to a great height, and its wings were spread from wall to wall. "

96
00:05:47,060 --> 00:05:48,699
Unambiguous: wings.

97
00:05:48,700 --> 00:05:50,239
Or maybe not?

98
